text:
#CovidVaccine experience:
Shot 1: surprised I didn't feel the injection. Sore shoulder for two days - less soreness than I often get from moving hay bales, digging in the garden, or sleeping on my side.
Shot 2: again, didn't feel it. No soreness at all afterward.
